216
00:22:59,613 --> 00:23:03,242
Even if I wasn't in the picture,
you'll never hold onto her.

217
00:23:04,373 --> 00:23:07,365
- Bloody hell!
- Maybe I didn't almost kill you enough.

218
00:23:08,533 --> 00:23:12,242
